SMTP PING

A simple, portable tool for measuring SMTP server delay, delay variation and throughput.

Build \w *nix:

	Requires cmake, should be quite easily ported to a Makefile

	 cmake .
	 make

Build \w Windows:

	Project file for Dev-C++ is included, should be quite portable to eg. VS.

Help:

	Feel free to contact <support@halon.se>
